Also, get me a cake.

30
00:01:59,140 --> 00:01:59,860
Low sugar.

31
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:04,620
I have some here.

32
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:06,100
Okay.

33
00:02:06,340 --> 00:02:07,500
Not bad, Mengnan.

34
