Everything I want, you have it today.

35
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,420
Come.

36
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,940
You even had this?

37
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:34,060
There's eye massager and fascia gun too?

38
